snippet.title: Stratospear : Showcase Fight
snippet.description:
Stratospear is a retro styled, bite sized 3d character action game, inspired by games like devil may cry and super smash bros. 

Made in 2 weeks for the 2022 32 bit game jam.

play it for free at https://rittzler.itch.io/stratospear
